<section class="screens" id="screens">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head centered">
      <span class="eyebrow">SCREENS</span>
      <h2>실제 베타 앱 화면.</h2>
      <p>지금 QR을 찍으면 보게 될 화면들입니다. 모두 실제 동작하는 베타 빌드의 스크린샷이에요.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="screen-rail">
      <div class="screen-item">
        <div class="phone-wrap">
          <div style="width: 265px; height: 573px; border-radius: 48px; background: #0b0f1a; padding: 8px; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(11,15,26,0.18), 0 0 0 1px rgba(11,15,26,0.10), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04); position: relative;">
            <div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 42px; overflow: hidden; background: #f2f2f7; position: relative;">
              <img src="/assets/screen-realtime.png" alt="실시간 매매" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
              <div style="position: absolute; top: 11px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 110px; height: 32px; border-radius: 20px; background: #000;"></div>
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 120px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4>실시간 매매</h4>
        <p>활성화된 종목과 조건을 한눈에. 가격 변동이 감지되면 카드 테두리로 알려줍니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="screen-item">
        <div class="phone-wrap">
          <div style="width: 265px; height: 573px; border-radius: 48px; background: #0b0f1a; padding: 8px; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(11,15,26,0.18), 0 0 0 1px rgba(11,15,26,0.10), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04); position: relative;">
            <div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 42px; overflow: hidden; background: #f2f2f7; position: relative;">
              <img src="/assets/screen-history.png" alt="주문 이력" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
              <div style="position: absolute; top: 11px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 110px; height: 32px; border-radius: 20px; background: #000;"></div>
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 120px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4>주문 이력</h4>
        <p>종목별 체결·실패 내역을 시간순으로 추적. 실패 사유까지 명확하게.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="screen-item">
        <div class="phone-wrap">
          <div style="width: 265px; height: 573px; border-radius: 48px; background: #0b0f1a; padding: 8px; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(11,15,26,0.18), 0 0 0 1px rgba(11,15,26,0.10), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04); position: relative;">
            <div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 42px; overflow: hidden; background: #f2f2f7; position: relative;">
              <img src="/assets/screen-portfolio.png" alt="포트폴리오" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
              <div style="position: absolute; top: 11px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 110px; height: 32px; border-radius: 20px; background: #000;"></div>
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 120px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4>포트폴리오</h4>
        <p>보유 종목과 투자자 수, 평균 변동률까지. 모델 포트폴리오와 비교해보세요.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
